A big moment towards making India #COVID19 free!

Phase 2 of #LargestVaccinationdrive targetting those above 60 years started today.

Hon'ble PM Shri @narendramodi took his COVID-19 vaccine dose at AIIMS appealing to all those who are eligible to take #vaccine.
